data.description: Immaculately maintained home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and is situated on a .25-acre lot. Spacious chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, ample work and storage space, and counter eating space. The dining area offers french doors opening to a back deck, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The primary bedroom has a private bath and walk-in closet, with convenient access to the laundry room. Skylights and vaulted ceilings highlight the generous living spaces and help to make a light and bright feeling.  Additional features include a storage shed, RV parking, and a 2-car carport. Home has been beautifully updated and offers a comfortable floor plan that makes for easy entertaining and living. Easy commute to JBLM
